Text:
Great! At long last someone with Scottish folk from the 60s & 70ies.
You wouldn't have The Corries & PAddier bell as well? Or Alex - drenched in Whiskey - Campbell?
ANYthing of British & Scotish Folk from that period would be most welcome.
Thanx for the three in Concert.
Can you seed please someone ,would love to see more of this kind of music cheers m8
